{"tid":1758172,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[永遠懷念]我最喜愛黃到發金女歌手 - 盧凱彤 Rockmui","createTime":"2019-11-27T01:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T07:20:42.000Z","uid":6721,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0e1106604e2116c88e42e187dcb5f0807cb41750","tid":1758172,"uid":6721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:46:38.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好忘記佢 - 盧凱彤<br />\n佢當年雨傘時勇於發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ntXTxEZjmbE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DntXTxEZjmbE&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=c7bcf679\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ntXTxEZjmbE</a><br />\n呢首歌係講抗爭嘅後生仔, 次次我都聽到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n//慘綠青年 你比我沒底線<br />\n行裝更多 年資更淺<br />\n離家更是遠 竟可以支撐到目前//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8rVMllAOvek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8rVMllAOvek&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=bc587d92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8rVMllAOvek</a><br />\n紅Van 雖然爛,但陳果好有眼光搵咗Ellen同Veegay做配樂(仲攞咗獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n//let the glorious days shed<br />\nwe've forgotten what we've had//<br />\n講緊被收返之後嘅香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2014年之後,佢同明哥 HOCC一樣被大陸封殺<br />\n專心喺台灣發展<br />\n佢上一隻碟《你的完美有點難懂並不代表世界不能包容》繼續寫社會議題<br />\n講環境講同性婚姻講自殺 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qlpr3xXyihI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQlpr3xXyihI&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=b47f5d75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qlpr3xXyihI</a><br />\n佢今年留低嘅作品當中, 我最鐘意嘅係呢首<br />\n呢個指鹿為蛇的時代, 希望我地一齊可以糾正返<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U-NYamM7NnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU-NYamM7NnY&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=f356b456\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U-NYamM7NnY</a><br />\n代你白頭, 亦同樣代逝世嘅手足白頭<br />\n希望你同手足在天上安好 遠離疾苦<br />\n遲一點 天上見"},{"pid":"b656edd0c1f5c9c78a5c0962b8c7423476a0726a","tid":1758172,"uid":6721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:48:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WW4-uiHUNlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWW4-uiHUNlA&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=abdff314\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WW4-uiHUNlA</a><br />\n好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42ac644673752c6eb81fa12b902e35304a4124e","tid":1758172,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/omEX1tT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FomEX1tT.jpg&h=57874f45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrdqqVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrdqqVy.jpg&h=1739302f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00a5ec3805cbd44f1582067906e961ad8a1d6ae2","tid":1758172,"uid":6721,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TpwfRL5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpwfRL5.png&h=0ca94bbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d74d44347368e04f445774ab30db95825d68d80","tid":1758172,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":6,"rep